name: Disharmony
description:
This artwork is intended to be collected once, and only once, by each and every collector.

Create a new disharmony on every click.
Collect the piece and it will come to life.
Collect more than one edition and it will collapse.

For collectors: Use the space bar or double click to start/stop the animation

Original artwork by Andreas Rau · Made with p5.js · Oslo, 2021

Disclaimer: This artwork is an experimental piece that relies on the Hicdex API to function as intended.
